SUB 39!!! Also puts me squarely in the Top 1000 for Celeste Any% which I can now brag to all of my friends about. 

Don't think I overly threw on any one section; main timelosses were:
- 7s in Rescue
- 10s in 1500M
- 14s in Rock Bottom
and cleaning up a bunch of other timelosses elsewhere.

Will probably take a break from speedrunning for a while (for real this time) in order to study for AP exams.

Oh and I also did Core because I felt like it, the time for that is 53:22.154. Don't think that's an actual category but whatever. You can tell how much I was sightreading Core :sob:
